William was born on November 19, 1933 and passed away on Tuesday, October 14, 2014.
William was a resident of Toledo, Illinois at the time of passing.
Visitation will be held on Friday, October 17, 2014 from 10:00 a.m. until the time of funeral services at 12:00 p.m. in the Walker Funeral Home, 5155 Sylvania Ave. (west of Corey Rd.). Interment will follow at Calvary Cemetery.
in lieu of flowers, that memorials be made to Hospice of Northwest Ohio.










